headline: Amgen: Imdelltra Data And Q1 Results Impress
summary: Amgen beat Q1 estimates with strong margins driven by Blincyto, Prolia, and standout Imdelltra growth, plus strength in obesity. See why AMGN stock is a buy.

headline: 1 Growth Stock Down 9% to Buy Right Now
summary: Eli Lilly's share price is down about 6.4% over the past year.  The pharmaceutical giant's weight-loss drugs continue to drive fast revenue and earnings growth.  Not many companies that have been around since the late 1800s can claim that they're growth companies.
